.el .ds Aq '
.TH wsp-template 1  "template " 
.SH NAME
template \- Manage workspace templates
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBtemplate\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage workspace templates
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
template\-new(1)
Create a new template
.TP
template\-ls(1)
List all templates [read\-only]
.TP
template\-show(1)
Show template contents [read\-only]
.TP
template\-rm(1)
Remove a template
.TP
template\-export(1)
Export a template to a file or stdout [read\-only]
.TP
template\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
